pageContext.claim: “For all of the political hacks out there, if I hadn't done my job well, & early, we would have lost 1 1/2 to 2 Million People, as opposed to the 100,000 plus that looks like will be the number.”
pageContext.analysis: The United States had just surpassed 100,000 cases -- and it was not the maximum because new cases continue to arise.
